      "body": "> Found this useful when replacing the bitcoin-qt target with the new bitcoin-qml one in the QML GUI staging branch.\r\n\r\nSomewhat tangential to the change here, but are we renaming `bitcoin-qt` to `bitcoin-qml`? Couldn't the GUI just stay named `bitcoin-qt`, given that the new QML code is just a drop-in replacement, and we aren't going to ship/have two different qt binaries at any point?",
